## Key Features
- Product catalog (Islamic books, religious items)
- Shopping cart and checkout
- Payment integration
- Order management
- User accounts
- Product search and filtering
- Categories and collections
- Reviews and ratings

## Important Context
- This is the E-COMMERCE project - Online store for Islamic products
- Primary language: French
- Target: Selling Islamic books and religious items
- Related to El Mouahidine organization

## Differences with Nadi Project
⚠️ **CRITICAL:** This is NOT the Nadi e-learning platform!
- Nadi = Educational videos & courses (streaming)
- Site Vente = Products & physical items (e-commerce)

## When Working on This Project
Always remember:
1. This is an e-commerce store, NOT an e-learning platform
2. Focus on products, cart, checkout, and orders
3. Payment processing and inventory management
4. Shipping and delivery features
5. Product catalog and search functionality

